realharmonium (1.0.1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * 4-layer reed synthesis engine (numpy + pygame).
  * Linux IIO accelerometer → bellows pressure mapping.
  * Full-terminal curses UI with animated bellows meter.
  * Sa drone mode with C4 + G4 + C5 resonance.
  * evdev fallback for older ThinkPad accelerometers.
  * Mouse/Space-bar bellows for desktops without sensors.

